{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(开设属于自己的\"性感带按摩诊所\"...这是我的梦想。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(我编写了一套看似合理的理论，制作了网站，还花了大笔钱请SEO公司推广。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(当然也发了传单。\"淫靡波动疗法\"。我是认真的。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(......但是开业当天的预约人数...只有一个。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(......被银行和消费金融公司拒绝后，我最终从一家叫\"龙金融\"的高利贷那里借了启动资金...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(还款期限是3个月后...12周。如果失败了，我就真的完了。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(......算了，不管怎样。今天来的女孩是我诊所唯一的希望。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "doubt_openmouth_sweat",
      "text": "......那个，打扰了......",
      "voiceFile": "story_day1_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "doubt_closemouth_sweat",
      "text": "欢迎光临！"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "doubt_openmouth_sweat",
      "text": "......我看到了传单...这里是按摩诊所，对吧？",
      "voiceFile": "story_day1_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "是的，没错。请进，不用担心。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "...好的。谢谢。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day1_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "那么，今天来这里有什么困扰吗？肩膀、背部，有什么不舒服的地方吗？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "嗯...最近，我的肩膀一直很僵硬...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day1_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "肩膀僵硬...我明白了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "(嗯，不意外。这女孩的胸部相当大...肯定很重...嘿嘿。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "我想了解更详细的情况，首先，请您放下东西，填写这份咨询表好吗？"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "另外，能告诉我您的名字吗？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "好的。我叫田中奈奈。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day1_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "我看看...困扰的地方......",
      "voiceFile": "story_day1_006",
      "cutInImage": "nana_writing"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "(哇！近距离看，她的胸部真的好大...！而且脸蛋也很可爱...中大奖了，嘿嘿...)",
      "cutInImage": "nana_writing"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "......那个，不好意思。这个...关于身体和、高、高潮经历...这种信息真的有必要吗...？",
      "voiceFile": "story_day1_007",
      "cutInImage": "nana_writing"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "当然有必要。为了让您放松，不只是身体方面，了解您的感官偏好也很重要。",
