    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "是、是这样吗...我...我从来没有填过这种东西...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day1_008",
      "cutInImage": "nana_writing"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "没关系。只要诚实地写，想到什么写什么就好。",
      "cutInImage": "nana_writing"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "我、我写完了...这样可以吗？",
