    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "谢谢。...嗯，我了解了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "那么，只是走个程序，能请您也在这份\"治疗同意书\"上签名吗？"
